                               ለእመ፡ 
                                 <sic>ሞትኵ፡</sic>
                               
                              ፴፡ ወ፫ቱ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ወ</supplied>ርቅ፡ ተሳየጥኩ፡ 
                                 <sic>ፈረስ፡</sic>
                               ፳፡ ወርቅ፡ ሀሎ፡ 
                                 <sic>ምስሌይ፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>አሒ፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>ሃኩ፡</sic>
                               ዘትሠመይ፡ 
                                 <sic>ሀገር፡</sic>
                               ቅሮጳን፡ ቅርብት፡ 
                              ሠሠብሬን፡ 
                                 <sic>ስንቆ፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>ሴ<supplied reason="omitted">ጥ</supplied>ኮ፡</sic>
                               ፲፡ ወአሀዱ፡ 
                              ፲ቱ፡ 
                                 <sic>ወቱ፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>መአልት፡</sic>
                               ስቴብር፡ 
                                 <sic>ተናዘዝን፡</sic>
                                  
                           </q>
                           <note>The note defines the distribution of the money belonging to the writer. 
                              The writer states to live in a city called Qǝroṗān or Śaśabren.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#1v" facs="0003"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear"/>
                           <q xml:lang="it">il grecero di pielli en 
                                 <sic>piassa</sic>
                               fornaro</q>
                           <note>The note is written in a <date>16th-century</date> hand.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#2v" facs="0004"/>
                           <desc type="CalendaricNote"/>
                           <note>Beginning of a calendar.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#71v" facs="0073"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              
                                 <sic>በወር<supplied reason="omitted">ኅ</supplied>፡</sic>
                               ማጅ፡ 
                                 <sic>፲ገአኩ፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>ነገር፡</sic>
                               ይቤ፡ እስቁፍ፡</q>
                           <note>The note is written in pale black ink. It states that the writer heard the sermon of the bishop on the 10th of May (cp. 
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">māǧ</foreign>) of an unspecified year.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#75v" facs="0077"/>
                           <desc type="CalendaricNote"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ር<supplied reason="omitted">እ</supplied>ሰ፡ 
                              አመት፡ 
                                 <sic>ወርሕ፡</sic>
                               መስከረም፡ 
                                 <sic>ብኢል፡</sic>
                              
                           </q>
                           <note/>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <locus target="#75v" facs="0077"/>
                           <desc type="CalendaricNote"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                             ር
                                 <sic>
                                    <supplied reason="omitted">እ</supplied>ስ፡</sic>
                               አመት፡ 
                                 <sic>ወርሕ፡</sic>
                               መስከረም፡ 
                              
                                 <sic>ብኢል፡</sic>
                               በዓረቢ፡ ቶት፡ ባቤ፡ ሐቶር፡ ክያክ፡ ጦቤ፡ እምሸር፡ በረምሃት፡ በረሙዲ፡ በሸስ፡ በኦና፡ አቢብ፡ ምስእሪ፡ ጅናር፡ ፍብራ፡ ማርስ፡
                           </q>
                           <note>The note contains the names of the months of the Copto-Arabic calendar, and those of the first three months in Italian 
                              (cp. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ǧǝnār, fǝbrā, mārǝs</foreign>).</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a8">
                           <locus target="#76v" facs="0078"/>
                           <desc type="Record"/>
                           <q xml:lang="it">
                              Il sig<supplied reason="explanation">no</supplied>r fiorauante ristillatore eccelle<supplied reason="explanation">n</supplied>tiss<supplied reason="explanation">im</supplied>o 
                              et particulare a dar remedii ad infiniti mali habita in napoli allo largo del castello nouo al portone di la casa del s<supplied reason="explanation">igno</supplied>r 
                              in istanza e questo ue lo auiso io ch'el trouiasi p<supplied reason="explanation">er</supplied> la u<supplied reason="explanation">ost</supplied>ra 
                              infirmita p<supplied reason="explanation">er</supplied>che sono stato dio gra<supplied reason="explanation">tia</supplied> Da lui 
                              guarito. Gio<supplied reason="explanation">uanni</supplied> Jac<supplied reason="explanation">obo</supplied> Matera. 
                           </q>
                           <note>The note was written in Italian in the <date>mid-16th century</date>. It states that 
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11376Fioravanti">Leonardo Fioravanti</persName> was living  near Castel Nuovo in Naples, and that he healed the 
                              one who wrote the note, a certain <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11377Matera">Giovanni Jacobo Matera</persName>.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a9">
                           <locus target="#77v" facs="0079"/>
                           <desc type="Record"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ስቴብር፡ ፲፡ ወ፰፡ መአልት፡ 
                                 <sic>ነገደነ፡</sic>
                              
                           </q>
                           <note>The note is written in black pale ink in the same hand as <ref target="#a2"/>. It states that the writer left on the 18th of September 
                           (cp. <foreign xml:lang="gez">sǝtebǝr</foreign>) of an unspecified year.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="a10">
                           <locus target="#78r" facs="0079"/>
                           <desc type="ProtectivePrayer"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ጰውሎ፡ ወሬዩዊና፡ ፈላዊና፡ ፈላፎት፡ ፈላፎት፡ ፈላፎት፡ ጻጻጻ፡ 
                                 <sic>አኃዚሆ፡</sic>
                               ፫ቃላተ፡ አልፍ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ኤፍ፡</supplied> 
                              ካፍ፡ በዝንቱ፡ 
                                 <sic>እስማት፡</sic>
                               
                              
                                 <sic>እሰር፡</sic>
                               እደዊሆሙ፡ ወእገሪሆሙ፡ ወአድክም፡ አብራኪሆሙ፡ 
                              ወአ<supplied reason="omitted">ጽ</supplied>ልም፡ አእይ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ቲሆሙ፡ 
                                 <sic>ለጸናሕያን፡</sic>
                               
                              ፍኖት፡ 
                                 <sic>ወለተትአጋልያነ፡</sic>
                               ንዋይ፡ 
                                 <sic>ወለካአውያነ፡</sic>
                               ደም፡ እስከ፡ አሐልፍ፡ አነ፡ ዮሀንስ፡ ምስለ፡ 
                              
                                 <sic>ኩሉ፡</sic>
                               ንዋይየ፡ ወጥሪትየ፡  
                           </q>
                           <note>The note was written by a certain Yoḥannǝs (perhaps <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11327Yohannes">Yoḥannǝs</persName>). It contains magical names to protect 
                              him along the way. The same prayer is also contained in <ref type="item" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet45#a1"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BAVet45#a1</span></ref>.
                           The word <q xml:lang="gez">ፌርቤዮ፡</q>, i.e. "february", is written in the lower margin of the same leaf.</note>
                        </item>
                    
